<!-- BLOQUE 05: Problema real -->
<div class="ce-shopify-block" data-root style="--accent:#ffd84a;--green:#18c964;--green2:#0aa650;--red:#ff3d4e;--muted:#a9b3c9;--mono:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif;color:#f8fafc;background:#050713;font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
  <section style="padding:76px 0;;font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif">
<div style="width:min(1120px,calc(100% - 32px));margin:0 auto;;font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif">
<div data-reveal="" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px);transition:all .7s ease;;font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif">
<span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:8px 13px;border-radius:999px;border:1px solid rgba(255,216,74,.25);background:rgba(255,216,74,.10);color:var(--accent,#ffd84a);font-size:12px;font-weight:900;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;;font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif">Problema real</span>
<h2 style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:clamp(32px,5vw,58px);line-height:.98;margin:15px 0;letter-spacing:-.05em;">Un pinchazo no debería dañarte el día.</h2>
<p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;max-width:720px;;font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif">Una grúa puede salir más cara que el kit completo. Y esperar a que aparezca una gomería abierta puede quitarte horas. Compra Exacta está pensado para resolver rápido los pinchazos pequeños cuando estás lejos de ayuda.</p>
</div>
<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.05fr .95fr;gap:24px;margin-top:36px;align-items:stretch;;font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif">
<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;;font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif">
<article data-reveal="" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(22px);transition:all .6s ease;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.13);background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,.09),rgba(255,255,255,.045));border-radius:24px;padding:24px;;font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif">
<div style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:16px;display:grid;place-items:center;font-size:22px;background:rgba(255,61,78,.12);border:1px solid rgba(255,61,78,.25);color:#ff7b88;margin-bottom:16px;;font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif">✗</div>
<h3 style="font-size:19px;margin-bottom:8px;;font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif">Grúa costosa</h3><p style="color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;font-size:14px;;font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif">Terminas pagando mucho por un problema pequeño y urgente.</p>
</article>
<article data-reveal="" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(22px);transition:all .6s ease .08s;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.13);background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,.09),rgba(255,255,255,.045));border-radius:24px;padding:24px;;font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif">
<div style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:16px;display:grid;place-items:center;font-size:22px;background:rgba(255,61,78,.12);border:1px solid rgba(255,61,78,.25);color:#ff7b88;margin-bottom:16px;;font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif">✗</div>
<h3 style="font-size:19px;margin-bottom:8px;;font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif">Taller lejos</h3><p style="color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;font-size:14px;;font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif">Pierdes tiempo buscando una opción abierta o esperando asistencia.</p>
</article>
<article data-reveal="" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(22px);transition:all .6s ease .16s;grid-column:1/-1;border:1px solid rgba(24,201,100,.3);background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(24,201,100,.12),rgba(255,255,255,.045));border-radius:24px;padding:24px;;font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif">
<div style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:16px;display:grid;place-items:center;font-size:22px;background:rgba(24,201,100,.14);border:1px solid rgba(24,201,100,.3);color:var(--green);margin-bottom:16px;;font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif">✓</div>
<h3 style="font-size:19px;margin-bottom:8px;;font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif">Kit en la guantera</h3><p style="color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;font-size:14px;;font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif">Lo llevas contigo para actuar rápido cuando el pinchazo sea reparable. Sin depender de nadie.</p>
</article>
</div>
<div data-reveal="" data-tilt="" style="opacity:0;transition:opacity .7s ease .1s;perspective:1100px;;font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif">
<div data-tilt-inner="" style="transition:transform .18s ease-out;transform-style:preserve-3d;border-radius:28px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);box-shadow:0 32px 95px rgba(0,0,0,.5);height:100%;min-height:340px;background:#000;;font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif">
<img alt="Neumático pinchado en la vía" src="{{ 'ce-neumatico-pinchado.png' | asset_url }}" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;;font-family:'Montserrat',Arial,sans-serif"/>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</div>